{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/transparent_steam_page_gif.gif?t=1737114589\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marooned on a remote island, troop leader Teal finds she has the ability to grow unique seedlings - endangered critters that love to gather the island's abundant resources. But the seedlings are threatened by greedy gnomes, who also happen to have all the missing parts to the island's only boat\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/SH_header_collect.png?t=1737114589\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Collect resources!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your loyal (but not always enthusiastic) troop's different abilities to gather a variety of resources!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/SH_header_farmgrow.png?t=1737114589\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Farm and grow!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plant and cultivate seeds to repopulate the island with the helpful seedlings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/SH_header_lvlup.png?t=1737114589\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Level up!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speed up production, gain new abilities and even automate by leveling up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/SH_header_fightback.png?t=1737114589\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Fight back!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Raise and arm sentry seedlings to defeat the oppressive gnomes and get your sprites back home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/SH_header_customize.png?t=1737114589\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Customize!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decorate to make the island your own! Spruce up your home and island with mix and matchable themed furniture.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/SH_header_befriend.png?t=1737114589\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Befriend!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get to know your fellow sprites! Chat, give gifts, and fulfill requests to grow your friendships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fun awaits  on Isle Fae.... see you there!\u2728</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/transparent_steam_page_gif_2.gif?t=1737114589\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> EARLY ACCESS ROADMAP\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/untitled_artwork-ynv9x9ee.jpg?t=1737114589\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Green Thumb","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2861360/5a2c0540194183f40f5ff617ab0a4679d55b60d9.jpg"},{"name":"Fast Learner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2861360/6462b0b6c64a16d